.github/workflows/daily-news.yml
yamlname: Daily News Aggregator

on:
  schedule:
    - cron: '0 7 * * *'
  workflow_dispatch:

jobs:
  run-news-aggregator:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    
    steps:
    - name: Check out repository
      uses: actions/checkout@v3
    
    - name: Set up Python
      uses: actions/setup-python@v4
      with:
        python-version: '3.11'
    
    - name: Install dependencies
      run: |
        python -m pip install --upgrade pip
        pip install -r requirements.txt
    
    - name: Run news aggregator
      env:
        ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: ${{ secrets.ANTHROPIC_API_KEY }}
        NEWS_API_KEY: ${{ secrets.NEWS_API_KEY }}
        EMAIL_ADDRESS: ${{ secrets.EMAIL_ADDRESS }}
        EMAIL_PASSWORD: ${{ secrets.EMAIL_PASSWORD }}
        RECIPIENT_EMAIL: ${{ secrets.RECIPIENT_EMAIL }}
      run: python news_aggregator.py

üîê SECRETS (Settings ‚Üí Secrets and variables ‚Üí Actions)
Add these 5 secrets:
Secret NameWhat to PutANTHROPIC_API_KEYYour Claude API key (starts with sk-ant-...)NEWS_API_KEYYour NewsAPI keyEMAIL_ADDRESSYour Gmail addressEMAIL_PASSWORDYour Gmail app password (16 characters)RECIPIENT_EMAILEmail to receive the digest

üìß Get Gmail App Password:

Go to: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
Generate password
Copy the 16-character code
Paste into EMAIL_PASSWORD secret


That's it! Copy these three things into GitHub and you're done! üöÄRetryClaude can make mistakes. Please double-check responses.
